write a program that deternines the two largest numbers inputted by the user

method
  initialize counter to 1
  initialize input 
  initialize largest
  initialize second_largest
  while counter is less than 11, so loop runs 10 times
    ask user for input
    store that input in input variable
    if counter is 1
      store input in largest
      store input in second_largest
    else
      if input is larger than largest
        sotre input in largest
      else if input is greater than second_largest
        store input in second_largest
    increment counter
  return largest and second_largest
